{"tid":189475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支爆來臨】輝山乳業股價暴跌九成　總部外有公安駐守","createTime":"2017-04-06T12:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T06:17:13.000Z","uid":79945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb01c9f3d0c590a0ce2a01deb1153ea9aa28a33","tid":189475,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-je4ntsKY7n8/WNTE5rLh6TI/AAAAAAAAKFU/RCQlPOv6n4kRli14Z8XUQ7GNdDNZU01jgCLcB/s1600/Screen%2BShot%2B2017-03-24%2Bat%2B3.02.45%2BPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-je4ntsKY7n8%2FWNTE5rLh6TI%2FAAAAAAAAKFU%2FRCQlPOv6n4kRli14Z8XUQ7GNdDNZU01jgCLcB%2Fs1600%2FScreen%252BShot%252B2017-03-24%252Bat%252B3.02.45%252BPM.png&h=5a60125e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】輝山乳業股價急挫後，公司位於瀋陽的總部守衛森嚴，董事長楊凱留守在內與債權人會面，有人來總部追討輝山欠款。 <br />\n<br />\n上月底，輝山乳業股價一個小時內急挫九成，然後停牌，到現在仍未復牌。 <br />\n<br />\n輝山乳業位於瀋陽的總部在股價急挫之後，有公安在大樓外駐守，並拉起封鎖線。外人要進入大樓都必定需要預約，外面的大街亦不時有公安車巡邏。 <br />\n<br />\n本台在清明節長假期後，於大樓外拍攝到相信是董事長楊凱進入大樓。據了解，自上星期開始，包括有來自各地的債權人來到瀋陽與楊凱見面。據見面的人形容，楊凱接見時神情輕鬆，但見面時間相當短，只有約10多分鐘，講明「欠債還錢，天公地道」。 <br />\n<br />\n在接待處，有曾經是輝山的員工來追討欠交社會保險。"},{"pid":"1127de3750425a8ebe5521a41bf9ca7d216a5d80","tid":189475,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ce8f46eb2dfafe7afb86d786623897d69fe763f","tid":189475,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:10:23.000Z","msg":"說好的賺左3億？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f6426165fa132d1ad6d362029abd9d50fd9301","tid":189475,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:04:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">據見面的人形容，楊凱接見時神情輕鬆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係啦，佢自己賺到fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8351640b3b6681e4adaa6c0f52bfa2fb54b7cfee","tid":189475,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"樓下有廢老仲話復牌就要狗衝去掃貨<br />\n仲話好抵買唔關你哋事，咪阻我發達添。"},{"pid":"6c76a1b5e13ba18aae1b3659a8c3d383aaa93d19","tid":189475,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:33:19.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b56ef4976f46e176ad9bb7f5f240b6ae2fed3d0f","tid":189475,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓下有廢老仲話復牌就要狗衝去掃貨<br />\n仲話好抵買唔關你哋事，咪阻我發達添。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下世都冇得復牌，拎黎做牆紙啦"},{"pid":"da513dcbaeeef5cf08648168939b741076fb0e98","tid":189475,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42acf2d8268e83dbdd957bf808fded0838e761a8","tid":189475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bd61d9ea6699b62107437463142364a22f9c08","tid":189475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95c54c41e272800e1d5bad144da544662c9d3b9","tid":189475,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>說好的賺左3億？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/finance/text/2017/0331/70884.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Ffinance%2Ftext%2F2017%2F0331%2F70884.html&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpApUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=137a92f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/finance/text/2017/0331/70884.html</a><br />\n借咗 400 億 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}